{"tid":1611043,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今晚林鄭月娥鐵定係度 咁多行動post 點解冇人講 ［一手料]","createTime":"2019-10-02T00:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:56:25.000Z","uid":64204,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9a6f7565975f3628af3ee9bcba8f9ee700995e75","tid":1611043,"uid":64204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:42:24.000Z","msg":"係呀 聽晚紅館有個垃圾show<br />\n「香港同胞慶祝中華人民共和國成立70周年文藝晚會」<br />\n我係入面其中一個工作人員<br />\n宜加係十月一號，夜晚十點半<br />\n全香港打到七彩 <br />\n我仲係紅館rehearsal緊個濕鳩show呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽晚  10月2號 <br />\n七點 <br />\n係紅館</span></span><br />\n推銷大灣區，黃絲豬嘅「民間特首」劉德華都會在場，<br />\n唱四首「中國人」果類撚屌歌。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥聽晚一撚定係到。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你嬲！？<br />\n佢聽晚出入順利，<br />\n邊個會驚你嬲！？<br />\n<br />\n聽日我要有二百萬人圍館。<br />\n要佢細嘗催淚彈，全民獅鳥嘅滋味！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec2ad7cd59ae73704a86a9dd63b507adb79f24a","tid":1611043,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3b5c37743bdbf761cb5cdb3ee7b3d9aa7cb4f0","tid":1611043,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"民間黃牛特首+姓黨特首"},{"pid":"3e37138f106c0f75afc9abef15b89c9f1012f687","tid":1611043,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T00:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c7a33f2b36d771d2bdb820effbdc0f4b10e2ec","tid":1611043,"uid